items.name: Four Arms
items.description:
Gives girls 4 arms, give or take. It lightly supports extra parameters like: from behind, top hands out, bottom hands out, top hands on face, top hands on head, bottom hands on hips, top hands covering breasts. It leans heavily into putting the top arms behind the head, so if you're not looking for that throw (t2up, top hands on head) in the negative prompt.

The best parameters I've found are a weight of 1-1.2, with added ((4arm):1.2), extra arms. You will need to do some cherry picking if you want the upper arms to be not behind the head. For img2img you can up the resolution and use a weight of 0.7ish for the lyco.

items.name: Miroslav Tichy
items.description:
Warning: contains both safe and unsafe content.

This model was trained by me in Dreambooth on 26 photos and then merged with text encoders of 3 other models.

Miroslav Tichy was a photographer who made thousands of secret shots of women in his hometown of Kyjov in the Czech Republic from the 1960s to 1985, using homemade cameras made of cardboard tubes, tin cans and other improvised materials. Most of them did not know they were being photographed. Some of them took competitive poses when they saw Tichy, possibly not realizing that the parody of the camera he carried with him was real. Write simple prompts (due to the small dataset) and don’t forget about the trigger “photo by Miroslav Tichy”.

Contains noise offset.

警告：包含安全和不安全的内容。

这个模型是我在 Dreambooth 上用 26 张照片训练的，然后和另外 3 个模型的文本编码器合并的。

Miroslav Tichy 是一位摄影师，他从 1960 年代到 1985 年，在捷克共和国的故乡 Kyjov 用纸板筒、易拉罐和其他临时材料制作的自制相机，偷拍了数千张女性的照片。他们中的大多数都不知道自己被拍了。有些人看到 Tichy 时会摆出竞争性的姿势，可能没有意识到他随身携带的相机的模仿品是真的。写一些简单的提示（因为数据集很小），并且不要忘记触发器 “photo by Miroslav Tichy”。

包含 noise offset.

Предупреждение: включает как безопасное, так и небезопасное содержимое.

Эта модель была обучена мной в Dreambooth на 26 фотографиях и затем объединена с текстовыми энкондерами 3 других моделей.

Мирослав Тихий был фотографом, который с 1960-х годов до 1985 года сделал тысячи тайных снимков женщин в своем родном городе Кийове в Чешской Республике, используя самодельные камеры, сделанные из картонных трубок, жестяных банок и других подручных материалов. Большинство из них не знали, что их фотографируют. Некоторые из них принимали конкурсные позы, когда видели Тихого, возможно, не понимая, что пародия на камеру, которую он носил с собой, была настоящей. Пишите простые промпты (из-за небольшого датасета) и не забывайте про триггер "photo by Miroslav Tichy".

Содержит noise offset.

items.name: Marin Kitagawa

Marin Kitagawa (My Dress-Up Darling) LoRA

Making models can be expensive. Do you like what I do? Consider supporting me on Boosty.

The main trigger word is Kitagawa but, as usual, you need to describe how you want her, as the model is not overfitted. Weight should be between 1 and 1.4 for the offset version (0.5-0.7 for the original one). There are also other target words, such as - ear piercing and earrings, but these are rather unstable tokens and they will have to be finalized in the inpaint, but you will find how to use the inpaint correctly in my Boosty. And also on my Boosty a lot of tutorial articles and nsfw content.

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

items.name: LEOSAM's [浮世絵/Ukiyo-e] 川瀬巴水 画风 Kawase Hasui Painting Style LoRA
items.description:
🤝如您有模型定制或其他合作、咨询需求，请联系Wechat: 13439222668。请简单注明来意，时间有限不闲聊哈，谢谢理解！

If you have any model customization or other collaboration and consultation needs, please contact Wechat: 13439222668. Kindly provide a brief description of your inquiry, as there's limited time and no time for casual chats. Thank you!

Ukiyo-e (浮世絵) is a unique art form originating from Japan's Edo period, characterized by rich colors and delicate lines through woodblock prints. Kawase Hasui (川瀬巴水, 1883-1957) was a renowned ukiyo-e master of Japan's Showa period. He excelled in depicting natural landscapes and was known for his exquisite craftsmanship and the inheritance of traditional Japanese art.

This LoRA model is trained based on 162 high-definition ukiyo-e works by master Kawase Hasui, aiming to imitate his intricate depiction techniques. By using this model, you can easily create ukiyo-e AI artworks with a strong Kawase Hasui style.

浮世绘（Ukiyo-e）是一种源自日本江户时代的独特艺术形式，通过木版画的方式表现出丰富的色彩与细腻的线条。川瀬巴水（Kawase Hasui，1883-1957）是日本昭和时期的一位著名浮世绘大师。他擅长描绘自然风光，以其精湛的技艺与对日本传统艺术的传承而闻名于世。

本LoRA模型基于川瀬巴水大师的162副高清浮世绘作品训练而成，旨在模仿其细致入微的描绘技巧。通过使用这款模型，您可以轻松创作出具有浓厚川瀬巴水风格的浮世绘AI作品。

浮世絵（Ukiyo-e）は、日本の江戸時代に起源を持つ独特な芸術形式であり、木版画を通じて豊かな色彩と繊細な線を表現しています。川瀬巴水（Kawase Hasui、1883-1957）は、日本の昭和時代の著名な浮世絵の巨匠です。彼は自然風景の描写を得意とし、その精巧な技術と日本の伝統芸術の継承で世界的に知られています。 このLoRAモデルは、川瀬巴水大師の162点の高解像度浮世絵作品を基に訓練されており、その緻密な描写技法を模倣することを目的としています。このモデルを使用することで、濃厚な川瀬巴水風の浮世絵AI作品を簡単に創作することができます。

items.name: Kamehameha [Concept]
items.description:
V1.0

updated with generated images, results can still be varied between checkpoints, but success rate increased in general, less artstyle bleeding observed. Adjust the weight and sampling method to test what work best for you. This lora currently still work best for human only at this moment, if you wish to change to a non-human character, inpaint may be required.

If you want to mix with a character Lora, I suggested you lower the weight of the character to 0.3-0.5 in txt2img first, increased it higher later in img2img.

Added tags for actions

  1. Charging: posture of holding energy ball next to hip

  2. Shoot: posture of shooting out, both hands in front of chest (rather unstable)

  3. Beam: posture of shooting out with beam blasting out, from side or from behind (very unstable)

Suggested tags for negative prompts

(dougi), spike hair, ((wristband))

V0.5

This Lora can teach your character how to perform kamehameha, this is still a bit unstable, sucess rate is about 40~70% depending on the checkpoints. Weight working rage from 0.8-1.2; this lora work alone best at 0.9.

The poses can be broken sometimes, i suggest that you find a pose generated you like and use that in controlNet (or use my displayed image for the pose).

If you don't see any energy ball when you pair with another character's lora, adjust this kamehaemeha lora to higher weight (0.9-1.2). img2img and inpaint may be needed depending on the other character's lora. The prompt in the display gallery will only get you general composition, further editing is needed in most cases.

Feel free to adjust the prompt to get the results; such as ((energy ball)) or (electricity) to enhance the effect. I suggest including night scene in prompt so the visual effect can stands out.

items.name: Scarlett Johansson in "Lost in Translation" (2003)
items.description:
Lost in Translation is a 2003 romantic comedy-drama film written and directed by Sofia Coppola. Bill Murray stars as Bob Harris, a fading American movie star who is having a midlife crisis when he travels to Tokyo to promote Suntory whisky. There, he befriends another estranged American named Charlotte, a young woman and recent college graduate played by Scarlett Johansson. Giovanni Ribisi and Anna Faris also feature. The film explores themes of alienation and disconnection against a backdrop of cultural displacement in Japan. Further analysis by critics and scholars has focused on the film's defiance of mainstream narrative conventions and its atypical depiction of romance.

items.name: Damian - Hentai University
items.description:
This is a LoRA for the character Damian, from Hentai University a game by Noodle Jacuzzi.

Damian's art is from the artists Himitsu Kessha Vanitas, the set -

Kaisha no Kawaii Kouhai (♂) o Hametakute Shouganai!

I've been working my way through making these for all the characters currently in the game, and sharing them in the Discord for HU, but figured I should also put them up here.

In general, I'm working from pretty limited image sets, so expect the results to be a bit wonky at times. And this is one of the boys, so the usual AI wonkiness with feminine boys comes into play as well.

I recommend a weight of around 0.5, possibly lower depending if you're combining the character LoRA with other styles/costumes/etc. along with tagging some defining characteristics of the character you're generating. Higher than that can really push the artist's original style, and may cause you issues.

All characters I train have a "character tag" added into the set to help generate them fairly reliably.

Damian has two looks. His normal, teacher look, and his streamer look. Both should work fine, as long as you tag for it.

Recommended LoRA Weight - 0.5 for fairly flexible, higher if you want more of the original artist's style, lower if it doesn't play nice with other loras.

Character tag - HUDamian, 1boy, flat chest,
Recommended tags - brown hair, short hair, yellow eyes, / blue hair, short hair, yellow eyes, toned,

I may have forgotten to check and tag eye color when doing my testing, but hey. If you want it to be "set accurate" be sure to tag.

I've got quite a backlog of these made up already, so I'll be uploading them on and off.

Check my other uploads as I put them out for more HU characters, and if you want any specific character put up soon, let me know.

Lisa Hannigan is an Irish singer-songwriter and musician. Lisa gained recognition as the former backing vocalist and frequent collaborator of Irish singer-songwriter Damien Rice. Lisa's collaboration with Damien Rice lasted for several years, but she eventually decided to pursue a solo career. In 2008, Lisa released her debut solo album titled "Sea Sew," which was critically acclaimed and received several award nominations. The album showcased her talent as a songwriter and highlighted her unique and delicate voice. Lisa's music often incorporates folk and acoustic elements, with introspective lyrics and atmospheric arrangements.
